Package: libpdcurses-mingw-w64-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: libpdcurses1-mingw-w64 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: A collection of routines used to create PDCURSES format graphics (mingw-w64, headers/libs)
 This Package contains the development files: headers and libraries.

Package: libpdcurses1-mingw-w64
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A collection of routines used to create PDCURSES format graphics (mingw-w64, runtime)
 This Package contains the runtime DLLs.
